data.name: ReadDisbursementTransactionType1
data.value: select top(1) DISB_TRAN_TYPE_ID, CODE, NAME, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TMST, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, DESCRIPTION from CKT_DISB_TRAN_TYPE where (CODE = @code) and (EFFECTIVE_DATE = @effectiveDate)

data.name: ReadDisbursementTransactionType2
data.value: select top(1) DISB_TRAN_TYPE_ID, CODE, NAME, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TMST, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, DESCRIPTION from CKT_DISB_TRAN_TYPE where CODE = @code order by CODE desc, EFFECTIVE_DATE desc
